Hey! What's up, man?

7
00:00:57.400 --> 00:01:01.180
I just want to thank you for not practicing your English.

8
00:01:02.110 --> 00:01:04.710
Since you decided to give up on your goal of becoming fluent

9
00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:09.370
I was able to get into the last available spot in Tony Kaizen's group classes.

10
00:01:10.370 --> 00:01:14.890
He's such a great teacher. He's the main reason I got into the exchange program.

11
00:01:16.350 --> 00:01:19.370
