12
00:01:20.830 --> 00:01:22.150
It's too bad you couldn't go with me.

13
00:01:24.380 --> 00:01:26.220
Anyway, you won't believe this.

14
00:01:26.850 --> 00:01:30.220
With all the stuff I learned from Tony I was able to express myself

15
00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.440
And make friends during my time in the U.S.

16
00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:36.380
I met some really cool guys who work for a multinational company,

17
00:01:36.650 --> 00:01:38.650
And they ended up helping me get a job there.

18
00:01:39.830 --> 00:01:44.630
The company sponsored my visa and now I'm living in sunny San Diego, California.

19
00:01:45.060 --> 00:01:48.900
Just 10 minutes from the beach. It really is like a dream.

20
00:01:50.600 --> 00:01:53.750
Moving to California was your dream, wasn't it?

21
00:01:56.110 --> 00:02:01.680
